data.title: SubgridClumping: Clumping factor for large low-resolution N-body simulations
data.name: SubgridClumping

evidence: "A Code to derive the parameters for the global, in-homogeneous and stochastic clumping model and then compute the clumping factor for large low-resolution N-body simulations"
"Our framework is devided into two main codes... AnalyseSubGridClumping.py... SimulateClumping.py" with usage via `python AnalyseSubGridClumping.py` and `python SimulateClumping.py`

Repository owned by GitHub user `micbia` and README links to a research publication: "See publication about this work https://arxiv.org/abs/2101.01712." indicating a research analysis code distributed via this repo.
